adith on Hijab: Women veiling themselves from men, even blind men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: While we were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Ibn Maktum was given permission to enter. He entered and that was after the command to veil. The Prophet said, \u201cVeil yourselves from him.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is he not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17097,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/03\/zina-do-not-touch-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":40573,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Adultery: Warning not to sexually touch an unrelated woman","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019qil ibn Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFor a nail of iron to be driven in the head of one of you would be better for him than to touch a woman who is not lawful for him.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 16910\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/05\/khulwa-relatives\/","url_meta":{"origin":40573,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Khulwah: Prohibition of men visiting married women alone","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBeware of entering the homes of women alone.\u201d A man from the Ansar said, \u201cWhat about sisters-in-law?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEntering upon them is deadly serious.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5232, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2172 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/18\/perfume-of-men-and-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":40573,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Perfume: The perfume of men and women","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 18, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe perfume of men is that which scent is apparent and color is hidden. The perfume of women is that which scent is hidden and color is apparent.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2787 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/women-permission-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":40573,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Wives need permission from husbands to fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, prohibited wives from fasting unless their husbands gave per